rcy-al-rahmah","tag-remembrance-al-dhikr","tag-supplication-al-dua"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-6uS","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":17151,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/12\/12\/haya-jannah-badha-nar\/","url_meta":{"origin":24978,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Haya: Modesty in Paradise, shamelessness in Hellfire","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 12, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cModesty is part of faith and faith is in Paradise. Shamelessness is part of insolence and insolence is in Hellfire.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2009 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":36289,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/05\/23\/dust-jihad-dukhan-jahannam\/","url_meta":{"origin":24978,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Jihad: Dust in jihad and smoke of Hell never combine","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 23, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cA man who weeps from the fear of Allah will never enter Hellfire, unless milk could return to its udder. The dust in the way of Allah will never combine with the smoke of Hell.\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32227,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/16\/hadith-on-arrogance-no-pleasure-to-be-received-standing\/","url_meta":{"origin":24978,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Arrogance: No pleasure to be received standing","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 16, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Mu\u2019awiyah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever is pleased to be received by men standing, let him take his seat in the Hellfire.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2755 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0645\u064f\u0639\u064e\u0627\u0648\u0650\u064a\u064e\u0629 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28831,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/05\/08\/tafsir-quran-ignorance\/","url_meta":{"origin":24978,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Tafsir: Warning not to interpret Quran without knowledge","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 8, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever speaks on the Quran witho